st of campaigns would drop back to an rate which ordinary people could once again run for elected office without huge money behind them. If we also combined this with balanced use (where each media outlet was required to air the exact same number of minutes--within 5%-- for each candidate in the race), then the money flowing in would be irrelevant. States could enact this without federal approval, and the courts could not overturn it based on free speech. Isn't this the effect everyone wants?</p>      </div>                    <a href="http://m.bd6.motherjones.com/mojo/2012/10/ben-jerrys-citizens-united-stamp#" class="dsq-comment-truncate-expand" onclick="return DISQUS.dtpl.actions.fire(&#39;comments.text.expand&#39;, 678238632);"> show more</a>        <a href="http://m.bd6.motherjones.com/mojo/2012/10/ben-jerrys-citizens-united-stamp#" class="dsq-comment-truncate-collapse" onclick="return DISQUS.dtpl.actions.fire(&#39;comments.text.collapse&#39;, 678238632);"> show less</a>                  </div>          </div>    <div class="dsq-comment-footer" id="dsq-comment-footer-678238632">      <div class="dsq-comment-footer-left">                    <a href="http://m.bd6.motherjones.com/mojo/2012/10/ben-jerrys-citizens-united-stamp#" onclick="return DISQUS.dtpl.actions.fire(&#39;comments.moderate.options&#39;, 678238632);">Moderate</a>            <span class="dsq-highlight">              <img id="dsq-highlight-678238632" src="./mobile_files/44-grey.png" onclick="DISQUS.dtpl.actions.fire(&#39;comments.highlight&#39;, 678238632);" width="16" height="16">            </span>              </div>            <div class="dsq-comment-footer-right">        <span class="dsq-user-like"><a href="http://disqus.com/motherjones-cfa7094aad8acebd4ecf3c6769cadcf9" onclick="return DISQUS.dtpl.actions.fire(&#39;profile.show&#39;, null, &#39;motherjones-cfa7094aad8acebd4ecf3c6769cadcf9&#39;); return false" target="_blank"><img src="./mobile_files/noavatar32.png" alt=""></a><a href="http://m.bd